## Backup Heartbeat

The "Backup Heartbeat" monitor is a push monitor. The pre-backup script on Seko-AI
pings the push URL after a successful backup. If no ping is received within 24 hours,
an alert is triggered.

Push URL: retrieve from Uptime Kuma after creating the monitor.
